		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">ISO 10303</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>ISO 10303</b> is an <a href="/wiki/International_Organization_for_Standardization" title="International Organization for Standardization">ISO</a> standard for the <a href="/wiki/Computer" title="Computer">computer</a>-interpretable <a href="/wiki/Representation" title="Representation">representation</a> and <a href="/wiki/Exchange" title="Exchange">exchange</a> of <a href="/w/index.php?title=Industrial_product_data&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Industrial product data (page does not exist)">industrial product data</a>. Its official title is "<i>Industrial automation systems and integration - Product data representation and exchange</i>", known as "<i>STEP</i>" or "<i>Standard for the Exchange of Product model data</i>".</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
<tr>
<td>
